<section id="content">

<blockquote>
	<q>It&#39;s easy to play any musical instrument.  All you have to do is touch the right key at the right time and the instrument will play itself.</q>
	<cite><a href="/author/443">J.S. Bach</a></cite>
	<footer>contributed by <a href="/contributor/347">Dan Powell</a></footer>
</blockquote>

